scraped_content.title: AWS Distribution Program
scraped_content.full_text: AWS Distribution Program Skip to main content AWS Partner Network‚Ä∫ AWS Partner Programs Are you an AWS Partner? Resell with AWS Grow your cloud business with an AWS Distributor Become an AWS Partner Log in to AWS Partner Central Overview The AWS Distribution Program enables AWS Partners to grow revenue opportunities by reselling AWS products and solutions. AWS Partners work with AWS Distributors to leverage their go-to-market support, offload billing and operations, receive funding benefits, and gain technical expertise. AWS Distributors go through a rigorous review process to ensure they provide AWS-specific partner development expertise and value-added services for your business. They support a wide range of businesses including system integrators (SIs), independent software vendors (ISVs), Managed Service Providers (MSPs), value-added resellers (VARs), digital marketing companies, hardware companies, and public sector organizations. Get Started Play Identify an AWS Distributor in your country to help you resell. Gain go-to-market support Receive pre-sales and post-sales support, training, marketing services, and enablement programs from your AWS Distributor to help you build and grow your AWS business. Scale your technical expertise Leverage AWS Distributors for their technical expertise with migrations, managed services, cloud optimization, and other complex initiatives. Drive operational efficiency Offload your billing and operations management to an AWS Distributor, enabling you to free up your teams to focus on positive customer experiences. Maximize your AWS Partner experience AWS Distributors help you progress as an AWS Partner and fully leverage all the Partner programs and benefits available to you. Find an AWS Distributor AWS Distribution Program Success Stories Loading Loading Loading Loading Loading Get Started 1 Join the AWS Partner Network Join the AWS Partner Network (APN) at no cost by creating your AWS Partner Central account. Become an AWS Partner 2 Enroll in the Services Path Enroll in the Services Path as a prerequisite to signing an AWS Distribution Seller Agreement. This Path is specifically designed for organizations that leverage AWS to deliver consulting, professional, managed, and resale services. Learn more about AWS Partner Tier requirements 3 Connect with an AWS Distributor Find an AWS Distributor in your country. To join the program, directly contact the distributor that best supports your business needs and begin onboarding. Your AWS Distributor will work with you to complete the AWS Distribution Seller Agreement. Not able to find what you are looking for? Contact the AWS Distribution Program team ¬ª Find an AWS Distributor 4 Start selling Upon completing your onboarding with your selected AWS Distributor, you can start selling AWS solutions immediately. Partner Testimonials ‚ÄúWhen you combine forces‚ÄîAWS working alongside an AWS Distributor working with a reseller‚Äîthat‚Äôs when innovation peaks and customers win big.‚Äù Anas Homaidani, Chief Commercial Officer, KUWAITNET Follow AWS Partner Network AWS Partner Newsletter Learn more APN Blog Learn more Partner Webinars Learn more APN LinkedIn Learn more APN Twitter Learn more
